verbose_text: Similarly, intra-articular triamcinolone acetonide reduced synovial inflammation scores in the MIA model (median = 1.0 (IQR 1.0-1.0)) compared to the vehicle injected MIA arthritic animals (median = 3.0 (IQR 3.0-3.0), P < 0.05).
